PROJECT_GOALS:
- Maintain a fork of NotEnoughUpdates-REPO that tracks upstream closely
- Automatically inject custom item categories and priorities for better REI ordering
- Improve usability for Hypixel SkyBlock item browsing (e.g. group Minions together)
- Treat all item JSON files as generated artifacts
- Never require manual editing of item JSON files
- Ensure all transformations are deterministic and idempotent
- Keep all custom logic isolated in Python scripts under /scripts
- Support frequent upstream updates without merge conflicts
- Enable full automation via GitHub Actions
- Preserve full compatibility with NEU and REI

ARCHITECTURE_RULES:
- Do not manually edit files in /items or /constants
- Only edit files in /scripts
- All custom behavior must live in /scripts
- Scripts must overwrite category/priority values, never increment or mutate existing ones
- Scripts must be safe to run multiple times with identical output
- No persistent state or caches outside version control
- Prefer simple, readable, rule-based logic over heuristics

TECHNOLOGY:
- Python 3.13 or greater
- Git (origin + upstream workflow)
- GitHub Actions for automation
- Static JSON processing only

OUT_OF_SCOPE:
- In-game editors
- Client-side REI plugins
- UI modifications to REI
- Non-deterministic sorting behavior
- Manual curation of individual items

ASSISTANT_GUIDANCE:
- Optimize for clarity, maintainability, and repeatability
- Avoid clever hacks or brittle logic
- Prefer explicit rules and category schemas
- Assume the repo updates frequently
- Assume scripts will be run automatically without human supervision